track_notes:
This a great route up the side of Cautley Spout Waterfall from The Cross Keys Temperance pub. There is roadside parking here. The walk is 5.85m with 2365ft ascent.
Times taken:
Cross Keys to Calf 100 mins
Calf to Yarlside 87 mins
Yarlside to Cross Keys 53 mins
Route completed with XYL Judy on Sat 21 March 2010 - both summits activated and qualified on 2m FM.
track_title: The Calf and Yarlside as one walk
